## Theme Root Overview ##

In a NOUVEAU theme, the theme root is reserved only for "top level" page templates are required WordPress files. At an
absolute minimum, the theme requires:

* style.css
* functions.php
* index.php

Although a few other files are included as well, for your convenience.

## Cleaning Up Your Theme Root ##

Depending on your project, there may be some extraneous files that are included with your package. The following files
can be safely deleted...

* GNU-LICENSE.txt
* MIT-LICENSE.txt
* README.md
* readme.txt
* screenshot.psd

If you are not using Compass/SASS, you can also delete:

* _compass (the entire folder)
* config.rb

Additionally, if you are not using CodeKit (why not!?) you can delete:

* codekit-config.json